{"tid":1788783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"重開 ［行動po]日本手足想推爆人主法案","createTime":"2019-12-19T03:08:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T12:12:06.000Z","uid":197468,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f9ab184a497e8a8ec93d146dc9aa6eb3ed064fb8","tid":1788783,"uid":197468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:08:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我知道各位手足去到日本，應該要盡情玩樂。但係想提醒大家五大訴求尚未達成，有眾多手足在還押中，每天有手足被自殺被失蹤，我哋香港人一定要繼績反抗！<br />\n所以而家喺日本嘅手足而家決定喺日本宣傳人權法案 希望到時大家多多支持</span><br />\n<br />\n[red] 如果喺大阪的手足，一齊過嚟以下日程：<br />\n日期：12月20日<br />\n時間：晚上6:30開始<br />\n地點：心齋橋，固力果公仔嗰度<br />\n行動：宣傳&lsquo;日本版香港民主及人權法案&rsquo;。到時會派文宣及叫口號［/red]"},{"pid":"fd5275123aecf027972a1a064cd16c58f4edabbe","tid":1788783,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:08:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2b2bf22898d78d96d2bd4b3b8922203fe8e8825c","tid":1788783,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:08:34.000Z","msg":"推！！！"},{"pid":"b74652650ef033b1e7e65c651c9a91c94cc39ce8","tid":1788783,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:08:54.000Z","msg":"香港金總終於接受網上會員申請啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1786114\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1786114</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"99e95d0b20d3bc3c52fa6bb2525e272db2ce6060","tid":1788783,"uid":197468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:09:14.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"59bc831a32b9d09f2d92675977aba6d3a52dcc34","tid":1788783,"uid":246359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:10:19.000Z","msg":"樓主有冇買衫"},{"pid":"42c7f1562347888b951af49e0cb38fd17ab77080","tid":1788783,"uid":277392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:10:39.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"d5dfd5b80b93d69d09a29966123c4e622abc2286","tid":1788783,"uid":197468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT